short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Filters and collapses pipelines in Go Continuous Delivery.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension allows you to collapse Go pipeline groups by clicking the header.  It also increases the size of the pipeline filter drop-down, and collapses the lists of pipelines in the filter to make management easier.
